<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= lang %>">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="content-language" content="en">
    <meta name="keywords" content="<%= __('meta.keywords') %>">
    <meta name="description" content="<%= __('meta.description') %>">
    <meta name="author" content="<%= __('meta.author') %>">
    <meta name="date" content="<%= __('meta.date') %>" scheme="YYYY-MM">
    <meta property="og:title" content="<%= __('profile.title') %>">
    <meta property="og:image" content="img/logo.png">
    <meta property="og:description" content="<%= __('meta.ogDescription') %>">
    <meta name="yandex-verification" content="6cfda41f74038368">
    <title>Submission Review</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/img/logo.png" type="image/png">
    <script src="/js/jquery-1.10.1.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            color: #333;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #1a202c;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        a {
            color: #3182ce;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
            color: #2b6cb0;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            margin-top: 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3182ce, #2b6cb0);
            color: #fff !important;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2b6cb0, #3182ce);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #1a202c;
            color: #cbd5e0;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer-link {
            color: #cbd5e0;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .footer-link:hover {
            color: #3182ce;
        }
    </style>
    <div style="max-width: calc(100vw - 30px);">
        <%- include('default/header.ejs') %></div>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>
            <%= message %>
        </h1>
        <p>We appreciate your contribution. Our team is currently reviewing your submission and will address it
            promptly.</p>
        <p>If you wish to make instant changes, please log in to your account.</p>
        <p>To learn more about our project, visit our official page at <a
                href="https://savchenkosolutions.com/study-guide"
                target="_blank">savchenkosolutions.com/study-guide</a>.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or suggestions, feel free to reach out to us at <a
                href="mailto:aliaksandr@melnichenka.com">aliaksandr@melnichenka.com</a>.</p>
        <a href="/<%= lang %>/register" class="btn btn-primary">Create account</a>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-container">
            <p class="footer-text">
                © <strong>Savchenko Solutions</strong>, 2023-2025
            </p>
            <p class="footer-text">
                All solutions are contributed by their respective authors (Savchenko Solutions contributors) and are based on original textbook content, which remains the property of the textbook authors. Unless otherwise noted, solutions are provided under the Creative Commons Attribution–ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-SA 4.0) license. Commercial use of any material requires written permission.
            </p>
            <p class="footer-text">
                <a href="mailto:aliaksandr@melnichenka.com" class="footer-link">aliaksandr@melnichenka.com</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>